short_description: allied schools is a high school based in rawalpindi, pakistan.
long_description: allied school is one of pakistan's best secondary schools. we focus on scholastic development, personal growth, and ethical enrichment of our students. within 10 years, allied schools has amassed 1075+ plus campuses across pakistan. all these campuses combined make up a student body of more than 5,20,000 students. over ten branches in rawalpindi/islamabad are run under mr. fahad inayat's administration. premier is a well-experienced administrator and an education practitioner who has accomplished many milestones in his journey of over two decades in the education sector. our administration takes pride in the quality of education we provide through a uniform system in place which stems from our thorough expertise in the area.
